data.description: Seller's offering $5000 concessions! Showings restricted due to seller in the middle of updating the flooring, paint, front door and landscaping. Excited to present this multi/split home tucked quietly within a cul-de-sac. With 1.1 acres, you are given a large amount of land in the front back AND the side of the home which is completely landlocked and yours with a peaceful view of the woods. Upon entry there is a newly installed front porch and steps along with an extended deck in the back for the above ground pool access! Inside on the main level features an open layout that divides the master bedroom as a split floor plan. Newly installed hardwood plank. A total of 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths on the main level and easy access to the deck. Great for any and all entertainment. Basement is a RECENTLY FINISHED BASEMENT. The sellers are the 2nd owner. The septic tank was serviced/pumped 3 years ago. With garage and exterior access, you have a sizable bedroom that can used as a private suite. A large and full bath with a standing shower with gorgeous tile work offers accessibility features. Less than 10 minutes from highway I-20 and a 45 minute straight shot to Atlanta. Come see today!
